Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别在我的店门口闹！滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 你也快走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这样待客的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,顾客？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来买东西的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样招呼客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,会砸了自己的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是顾客？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 你要买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买两个水罐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-那孩子是什么人？\N-是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫音松 是孩子王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个熊孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少跟我开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要带两个水罐回家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没法拿两个大水罐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己就能拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我就卖给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,三文钱一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这点钱只够买块糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让大人哑口无言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看你怎么把水罐拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己一个人拿两个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还等什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拿不走的话 我可不会轻饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打碎才方便拿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,水罐被我买下就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎样都可以 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是 那孩子说得有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你被小孩子耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好机智的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-好！\N-真有你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 你听着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说要一次性拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说我会拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的我再来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先帮我留着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他将来一定能做大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚吃香鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很贵吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,您不必担心这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就恭敬不如从命 享受美食了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 父亲正在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么不懂礼数！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可他总是在忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然用球砸母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-来抓我吧！\N-别跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个都消停会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别生气了 来跟我玩球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,训得太狠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下 头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能和您说句话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,审问不顺是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是石川五兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们根据彦十的线报抓捕了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他巧言善辩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说我盗窃 就拿出证据来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们肯定是因为有线人的证词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个线人以前就是贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们居然信他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑我一介良民？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们作何解释？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,彦十
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定他是石川五兵卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他有烫伤的疤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是他没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,烫伤的疤痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总之毒蛇新兵卫那伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奸淫掳掠 无恶不作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果五兵卫在江户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定会有所动作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-对吧 彦十？\N-正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找到他们藏匿的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,弄清楚他们打算在何时何地下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,必须让他张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我们明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会也没辙了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,佐岛正在审问他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但感觉也没什么希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要会会这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很久以前见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是他！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,音松！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他将来一定能做大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,活该！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大人都没脑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是我家里那位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真搞不懂她喜欢他什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才就看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是不是…\N-住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,伤疤是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不关你的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,音松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲四年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他出去赌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,估计又会输光了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给 拿钱快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在 他就不会闹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,臭小子 你看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你当我是傻瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么看！该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听说过本所鬼铁吗？就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对我发誓再也不动音松一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,发誓！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不碰音松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他再打你 就来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到本所的长谷川家找我 记住了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,音松 究竟是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见 音松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎会沦落至此？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道这都是因为你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后 那家伙收敛了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但没坚持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他就又对我拳打脚踢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为被你警告过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以出手更重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没报官吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,报了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们根本不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,案件被当作家庭纠纷处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼平先生 我甚至去你的大宅找过你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,按照和你的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但门卫见我衣衫褴褛把我赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是头儿那时被委派京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-别说了 小柳\N-可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是工作委派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,与音松无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找鬼铁了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！别打了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我出丑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,求你别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不该生你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后 我只身逃离了江户
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我才12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你明白了吧 鬼平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让我变成今天这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是忘恩负义！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 酒井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要杀就杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,除此以外 我一个字也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个五兵卫也是个可怜人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,12岁就遭遇那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他只能走上犯罪的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在替他辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他到底在想些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂！\N-这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是鬼平的妻儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他妻子40多岁还能生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可真有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺是盗贼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被头儿和夫人收养了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小柳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们视她如己出？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小柳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,见过阿顺小姐后我才醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打算要抢劫的人家也许也有小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望再有孩子经历痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天会招供
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想请你帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么吗？说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就算从远处也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我再见见阿顺吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那样能让我坚定信念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这可爱的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要牢牢记住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,住口 五兵卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你一件事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,长谷川平藏不是你的亲爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的亲爹是个贼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样 所以我能理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的养父根本不在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他根本就不喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你想到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 别听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别信他的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,此事都是因我们粗心所致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是属下的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我该看好阿顺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 她早晚要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,彦十看着呢 这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还是让别人陪着她比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一不留神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子大概这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找一个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细找！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真想看看他现在的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,开始审讯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天跟你女儿说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 醒醒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没抓到香鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要给我抓香鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是父亲亲生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别管别人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 你就是我的宝贝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们买点香鱼回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果当年也有人照顾你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们被逮捕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,毒蛇新兵卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,束手就擒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是火付盗贼改方的长谷川平藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗者格杀勿论！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你决定受死？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以活下来 为我做事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我活够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不到30岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是年龄的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你有最后的愿望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能让鬼平做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了 音松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,头儿的心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,自从五兵卫被行刑就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,已经五天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定很自责
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出去玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,阿顺 你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 阿顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,（下集预告）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,平藏父亲的遗物烟管被盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,平藏偶然找到了它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下集再见
